    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "SUBJECT: FLYING SAUCERS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "The matter of flying saucers was discussed by",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "Special Agent [REDACTED] with Major General",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "Joseph F. Carroll of OSI on October 18, 1950, at which",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "time Major General Carroll advised that insofar as he has",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "been able to determine the Air Force is not working on",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "any type of \"flying saucer\" or \"flying disk\". General",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "Carroll stated that the Air Force is working on high",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "altitude rockets and jet aircraft. He stated these",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "experiments may account for some of the reports concerning",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "flying saucers but that the Air Force is not apparently",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "working on anything which is the cause of the many flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "saucers reports. He stated that the Air Force program",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "for investigating reports concerning flying saucers, etc.,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "has been reconstituted at Wright Field and that any perti-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "nent information of interest coming to his attention will",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "be furnished to the Bureau.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "status": "blank"
    },
